1.caption_en:
Caption:
A slide comparing "World before Platforms" and "World with Platforms," showing platform companies (e.g., Uber, Airbnb, Facebook, YouTube) moving to a central orchestrator position around the consumer. The right-hand column lists three pressures on incumbents: losing contact with consumers & market insights, shrinking margins for product & asset-heavy companies, and pressure to build connected services for integrated consumer experiences.
